# Sitemap (auto-generated by next-sitemap at build time)
# Step 6-G: sitemap.xml and robots.txt are now committed.
# - robots.txt is hand-written with AI crawler policies (next-sitemap.config.js
#   has generateRobotsTxt: false to avoid overwriting it on build).
# - sitemap.xml is regenerated on every `pnpm build` via `postbuild`; we still
#   commit it so it's visible in PRs and stays present without a fresh build.

